snippet.title: Sinfeld Remastered - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1710910/Sinfeld_Remastered_Deceased_and_Assist_Demo/

We have officially begun development on the story mode of Sinfeld Remastered and want to kick it off by releasing a fun fan experience based on the original that started it all.... "Sinfeld Chronicles" from 2020.

Download the "Deceased and Assist" mission demo now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1710910/Sinfeld_Remastered_Deceased_and_Assist_Demo/
